            ],
            "weighting": "<dd> P/F Required to pass the course </dd>",
            "due_date": "<dd><p> 24/08/2026</p>\n<p> 21/09/2026</p>\n<p> 26/10/2026</p></dd>",
            "learning_objectives": "L04, L06",
            "mode": "Written",
            "category": "Quiz",
            "task_description": "<div class=\"collapsible collapsible--text\">\n<p>Students need to complete the online cultural safety module before the end of semester <strong>and complete the short answer quiz for this during at least one of the in-tutorial quizzes</strong>. Students will be automatically enrolled in the LearnX course for the whole Faculty with a link available on the PSYC1030 page available for their study.</p>\n<p><strong>Students must complete module content (Learn X) and the quiz (via the in-tutorial quizzes)</strong>. This task requires completing the learning module content as well as passing 1 short answer question that will be available to answer during each of the three in-tutorial quizzes. Students quiz answers will be marked on whether their response is appropriate, evidenced by module content and resources. Inappropriate or derogatory/disrespectful answers, or failing to sufficiently engage with the module content, will fail this assessment. Students may retake the assessment during each in-tutorial quiz. If, for example, a student fails the cultural safety short answer during the first quiz, they can try again in the second quiz and so forth.</p>\n<button class=\"collapsible__toggle\">\n<span class=\"collapsible__open link--icon icon--standard--arrow-down-1\">Read full task description</span>\n<span class=\"collapsible__close link--icon icon--standard--arrow-up-1\">Hide full task description</span>\n</button>\n</div>",
            "submission_guidelines": "<p>Submission will be alongside the other in-tutorial quizzes.</p>",
            "deferral_or_extension": "<p>You cannot defer or apply for an extension for this assessment.</p>",
            "late_submission": "<p>No late submission as assessment must be completed in class</p>",
            "additional_info": "<p>You cannot defer or apply for an extension for this assessment.</p>"
        },
